      "message": "Patch Set 2: Code-Review-1\n\n> Actually, currently max_sectors_kb=0 doesn't mean it won't do\n > nothing, instead it read existed @max_sectors_kb and write it\n > again with it (even it doesn't change anything)\n > \n > I am not sure whether this could cause messy value, maybe we could\n > ask Arthur to test if this could Solve His problem for DDN exscaler\n > problem.\n\nIf Artur has a problem, it would be useful to have a DDN or EX ticket open and linked to LU-12297 to know what the problem is.\n\n > Or we could improve the case that max_sectors_kb=0 did nothing?\n\nI think that is a much better way to fix the problem.  It will fix the problem just by upgrading Lustre without the need to change the configuration as well, and for admins to learn a new configuration option.",
